To build a debian/Ubuntu package for crackle, run:

 dpkg-buildpackage -us -uc

 To update the version, see:
   debian/changelog

   A new entry can be made with:

     export DEBFULLNAME="James Marsh"
     export DEBEMAIL="james.marsh@manchester.ac.uk"
     dch -i

The packages will be placed in the parent directory to this README.debian
